snippet.title: Mario Kart 8 Deluxe - Booster Course Pass Wave 5 - Nintendo Direct 6.21.2023
snippet.description:
Wave 5 of the Mario Kart 8 Deluxe - Booster Course Pass races in this summer with 8 more courses, including the all-new Squeaky Clean Sprint, and 3 more returning characters!

• Petey Piranha
• Wiggler
• Kamek

Get the Booster Course Pass today: https://mariokart8.nintendo.com/booster-course-pass/
